[[丹尼爾·克雷格|丹尼爾·克雷格]]賦予了他[[詹姆士·龐德|詹姆士·龐德]]一角，卡維爾表示有意接手<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.newshub.co.nz/entertainment/superman-star-keen-to-try-bond-2013042306 |title=Superman star keen to try Bond |work=Newshub |date=2013-04-23 |accessdate=2018-01-27 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108124446/https://www.newshub.co.nz/entertainment/superman-star-keen-to-try-bond-2013042306 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。由於[[湯姆·克魯斯|湯姆·克魯斯]]不得不拍攝《[[不可能的任務：失控國度|不可能的任務：失控國度]]》而放棄和[[艾米·漢默|艾米·漢默]]主演《[[紳士密令|紳士密令]]》中出演，卡維爾被找來取代克魯斯，該片將於2015年上映<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2013/06/04/man-of-steel-henry-cavill/2384785/ |title='Man of Steel' star Henry Cavill needs nerves of steel |accessdate=2014-02-07 |archive-date=2020-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801142201/https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2013/06/04/man-of-steel-henry-cavill/2384785/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Patricia Didelot |url=https://www.inquisitr.com/688284/henry-cavill-confirms-his-role-in-the-man-from-u-n-c-l-e-and-shares-more-about-man-of-steel/ |title=Henry Cavill Confirms His Role In 'The Man From UNCLE' And Shares More About 'Man Of Steel' |publisher=Inquisitr.com |date=2013-06-05 |accessdate=2013-06-23 |archive-date=2020-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201001195950/https://www.inquisitr.com/688284/henry-cavill-confirms-his-role-in-the-man-from-u-n-c-l-e-and-shares-more-about-man-of-steel/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://entertainment.inquirer.net/97421/from-man-of-steel-to-man-from-u-n-c-l-e |title=From 'Man of Steel' to 'Man From UNCLE' |publisher=Entertainment.inquirer.net |date=2013-06-06 |accessdate=2013-06-23 |archive-date=2013-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130612020713/http://entertainment.inquirer.net/97421/from-man-of-steel-to-man-from-u-n-c-l-e |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年，宣布卡維爾將出現在電影《[[長城_(電影)|長城]]》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://screenrant.com/great-wall-edward-zwick-zhang-ziyi-sandy-178651/ |title='The Great Wall' Lands New Start Date; Zhang Ziyi Being Courted to Star |publisher=Screenrant.com |date= |accessdate=2013-06-23 |archive-date=2016-10-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161015005727/http://screenrant.com/great-wall-edward-zwick-zhang-ziyi-sandy-178651/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但後來並無參與演出。

