== 個人生活 ==
2011年5月3日，卡維爾與[[場地障礙賽|場地障礙賽]][[馬術|馬術]]職業選手女友{{link-en|愛倫·惠特克|Ellen Whitaker}}[[訂婚|訂婚]]，但最終分手收場<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/showbiz/news/a400662/man-of-steel-henry-cavill-ellen-whitaker-end-engagement.html |title='Man of Steel' Henry Cavill, Ellen Whitaker end engagement |work=digitalspy.co.uk |date=2012-08-20 |accessdate=2013-08-28 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924172356/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/showbiz/news/a400662/man-of-steel-henry-cavill-ellen-whitaker-end-engagement.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/henry-cavill-ellen-whitaker-secretly-end-engagement-2012208 |title=Henry Cavil, Ellen Whitaker secretly end engagment |work=usmagazine.com |date=2012-08-20 |accessdate=2013-08-28 |archive-date=2021-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125023745/https://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/henry-cavill-ellen-whitaker-secretly-end-engagement-2012208/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，之後與[[武術家|武術家]]出身的[[義大利裔美國人|義大利裔美國人]]、演出《[[玩命關頭6|玩命關頭6]]》女演員[[吉娜·卡拉諾|吉娜·卡拉諾]]交往。2013年5月，他與女友卡拉諾分手。2015年，卡維爾又與塔拉·金（{{lang|en|Tara King}}）交往，於2016年分手<ref>{{cite web|title=Superman star Henry Cavill, 33, 'dumps his student girlfriend Tara King, 19, after less than a year together|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-3591576/Superman-star-Henry-Cavill-33-dumps-student-girlfriend-Tara-King-19-year-together.html|accessdate=2017-02-10|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126000036/https://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-3591576/Superman-star-Henry-Cavill-33-dumps-student-girlfriend-Tara-King-19-year-together.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在此前，他也曾與[[凱莉·庫柯|凱莉·庫柯]]短暫交過往<ref>{{cite web|title=Kaley Cuoco-Sweeting Talks 10-Day Fling With Henry Cavill, Former Romance With Johnny Galecki and Marriage to Ryan Sweeting|url=http://www.eonline.com/uk/news/527160/kaley-cuoco-sweeting-talks-10-day-fling-with-henry-cavill-former-romance-with-johnny-galecki-and-marriage-to-ryan-sweeting|accessdate=2017-02-10|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107193037/https://www.eonline.com/uk/news/527160/kaley-cuoco-sweeting-talks-10-day-fling-with-henry-cavill-former-romance-with-johnny-galecki-and-marriage-to-ryan-sweeting|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2016年開始練習[[巴西柔術|巴西柔術]]，曾在倫敦的{{link-en|羅傑·格雷西|Roger Gracie}}學院接受訓練<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.bjjee.com/featured/superman-actor-henry-cavill-trains-jiu-jitsu-w-roger-gracie/ |title=Superman Actor Henry Cavill Trains Jiu-Jitsu w/ Roger Gracie |website=BJJ Eastern Europe |access-date=2018-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171128125015/https://www.bjjee.com/featured/superman-actor-henry-cavill-trains-jiu-jitsu-w-roger-gracie/ |archive-date=2017-11-28 |dead-url=no}}</ref>。

卡維爾從小就一直是個狂熱的[[電腦遊戲|電腦遊戲]]玩家<ref name="pcgame">{{Cite web |url=https://www.pcgamer.com/henry-cavill-rejects-your-notion-of-a-gaming-man-cave/ |title=Henry Cavill rejects your notion of a 'gaming man cave' |first=Andy |last=Chalk |date=2020-01-03 |website=PC Gamer.com |access-date=2021-04-07 |archive-date=2021-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210419231716/https://www.pcgamer.com/henry-cavill-rejects-your-notion-of-a-gaming-man-cave/ }}</ref><ref name="gqgaming">{{Cite web |url=https://www.gq-magazine.co.uk/culture/article/henry-cavill-interview-2019 |title=Henry Cavill: Gaming on my own is much more fun than going out. |first=Sam |last=White |date=2019-12-19 |website=British GQ |access-date=2021-04-07 |archive-date=2021-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210525052900/https://www.gq-magazine.co.uk/culture/article/henry-cavill-interview-2019 }}</ref>。曾因專心遊玩《[[魔獸世界|魔獸世界]]》而沒空理會史奈德的電話，讓他差點錯失超人一角<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.polygon.com/2016/4/2/11353442/henry-cavill-was-too-busy-playing-warcraft-to-answer-a-call-to-play |title=Henry Cavill was too busy playing Warcraft to answer a call to play Superman |last=Good |first=Owen S. |date=2016-04-02 |website=Polygon |access-date=2020-04-28 |archive-date=2021-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210506093546/https://www.polygon.com/2016/4/2/11353442/henry-cavill-was-too-busy-playing-warcraft-to-answer-a-call-to-play }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.wanuxi.com/henry-cavill-%E5%B7%AE%E7%82%B9%E5%9B%A0%E4%B8%BA-%E9%AD%94%E5%85%BD%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C-%E8%80%8C%E6%B2%A1%E7%9A%84%E5%81%9A%E8%B6%85%E4%BA%BA/|title=Henry Cavill 差点因为 魔兽世界 而没的做超人|author=Strifey|work=Wanuxi 游戏网|date=2016-04-04|accessdate=2021-04-04}}</ref>。在拍《獵魔士》時將自己對《[[巫师_(游戏)|巫師]]》系列遊戲的熱愛作為飾演利維亞的傑洛特的動力。曾將《[[全面战争系列|全面战争]]》列為他的最愛<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-witchers-henry-cavill-would-rather-play-total-/1100-6472429/ |title=The Witcher's Henry Cavill Would Rather Play Total War: Warhammer 2 Right Now |date=2019-12-24 |website=Gamespot |access-date=2020-05-21 |archive-date=2021-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210418081314/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-witchers-henry-cavill-would-rather-play-total-/1100-6472429/ }}</ref>。他也是《[[战锤40000|战锤40000]]》的粉絲<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.pcgamer.com/henry-cavill-is-spending-his-quarantine-time-painting-warhammer-miniatures/ |title=Henry Cavill is spending his quarantine time painting Warhammer miniatures |first=Andy |last=Chalk |date=2020-04-13 |website=PC Gamer.com |access-date=2021-04-07 |archive-date=2021-06-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210601174842/https://www.pcgamer.com/henry-cavill-is-spending-his-quarantine-time-painting-warhammer-miniatures/ }}</ref>。

卡維爾亦是{{link-en|澤西野生動物信託基金|Durrell Wildlife Conservation Trust}}的代表發言人<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.comicbookmovie.com/fansites/Darktower/news/?a=105617 |title=Henry Cavill, A True Hero To The Wildlife |publisher=ComicBookMovie.com |date= |accessdate=2014-08-08 |archive-date=2015-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923205708/http://www.comicbookmovie.com/fansites/Darktower/news/?a=105617 |dead-url=no }}</ref>和皇家海軍陸戰隊慈善信託基金的大使。卡維爾目前住在[[倫敦市|倫敦市]]的[[南肯辛頓|南肯辛頓]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Why Henry Cavill is more Clark Kent than Superman|url=http://failover-www.thesundaytimes.co.uk/style/living/article1676212.html|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161006072720/http://failover-www.thesundaytimes.co.uk/style/living/article1676212.html|archivedate=2016-10-06|accessdate=2017-02-10}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Henry Cavill Gets Real About the Financial Perks of Being an Actor: 'I'm Not Just Doing This for the Art'|url=http://www.etonline.com/news/184237_henry_cavill_gets_real_about_the_financial_perks_of_being_an_actor_i_m_not_just_doing_this_for_the_art/|accessdate=2017-02-10|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125062544/https://www.etonline.com/news/184237_henry_cavill_gets_real_about_the_financial_perks_of_being_an_actor_i_m_not_just_doing_this_for_the_art|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Henry Cavill on Batman v Superman, Dunhill suits and stockbroking|url=http://www.squaremile.com/the-interview-henry-cavill/|accessdate=2017-02-10|archive-date=2017-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170921000607/https://www.squaremile.com/the-interview-henry-cavill/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

